data.description: WAIT!  Did you say a Richmond plan on a Greenbelt Lot!!  And a Community POOL! This Richmond Plan has 3 bedrooms w/ an office or 4th bedroom! A meticulously kept 3-year-old home is better than new and sure to check all your boxes!  Large bedrooms, including the office/4th bedroom!  Soft-close drawers, granite counters, walk-in pantry, and stainless-steel appliances are featured in the kitchen.  Oversized tiled shower, double sinks, and a spacious walk-in closet. 2-inch blinds are throughout, and tile on a brick pattern for that extra touch in all common areas of the home. Both bathrooms have tile shower surrounds and granite counters.  This home also includes some smart home features: a video doorbell, a smart light switch by the front door, app-accessible garage door, front door keypad, SmartLocks and a programable thermostat. Pleasant Hill subdivision is located on the West side of town close to RELLIS campus, Downtown Bryan and has easy access to this growing part of the community.
